00:00:00.780 --> 00:00:02.480
welcome in to Luca's Kitchen

00:00:03.120 --> 00:00:06.840
today we will prepare the chowder

00:00:33.620 --> 00:00:35.700
for 2 people we need:

00:00:35.880 --> 00:00:37.600
10 tomatoes cut

00:00:39.260 --> 00:00:42.180
same mussels 

00:00:44.100 --> 00:00:46.100
parsley

00:00:47.060 --> 00:00:51.500
gurnard or redfish

00:00:52.580 --> 00:00:56.100
1/2 Slice of swordfish

00:00:56.280 --> 00:00:58.280
10 shrimps

00:00:58.500 --> 00:01:01.160
1/2 cuttlefish

00:01:02.400 --> 00:01:06.880
salt and withe wine

00:01:08.460 --> 00:01:10.800
let's start

00:01:13.180 --> 00:01:17.020
started to cook the tomatoes in a pan

00:01:25.180 --> 00:01:30.580
and cook your mussels in a pot

00:01:32.034 --> 00:01:36.214
as soon as they open, turn off the flame

00:01:39.073 --> 00:01:42.693
cook the tomatoes for 5 minutes

00:01:46.634 --> 00:01:49.614
 put the tomatoes aside

00:01:52.340 --> 00:01:55.980
now filter the mussels

00:02:14.140 --> 00:02:17.320
remove the shell

00:02:17.900 --> 00:02:20.820
but  leave, 3 or 4 entire (for decoration)

00:02:25.360 --> 00:02:29.700
put celery, carrot and onion in a pot

00:02:30.160 --> 00:02:32.160
with some oil

00:02:32.740 --> 00:02:35.620
cook for less than a minute

00:02:37.400 --> 00:02:41.600
add the scraps of fish

00:03:01.100 --> 00:03:03.080
reduce heat

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:11.320
add a glass of withe wine

00:03:25.400 --> 00:03:26.660
cover it 

00:03:29.020 --> 00:03:32.740
and leave on  fire for 15/20 minutes

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:35.720
on a low flame

00:03:38.420 --> 00:03:42.140
after I have filtered our fish souce 

00:03:44.180 --> 00:03:48.320
now proceed to final stage

00:03:52.220 --> 00:03:56.540
put a pot on the stove with olive oil and some garlic

00:03:57.860 --> 00:04:01.140
add all our see products

00:04:02.253 --> 00:04:06.753
swordfish, shard (or redfish), shrimp and squid

00:04:18.157 --> 00:04:21.077
moderate heat

00:04:29.720 --> 00:04:33.340
add a glass of withe wine

00:04:38.140 --> 00:04:40.780
a glass of water 

00:04:50.520 --> 00:04:54.940
add the sauce obtained previously from fish scraps

00:05:00.360 --> 00:05:03.520
tomatoes previously cooked

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:08.340
mussels

00:05:21.553 --> 00:05:24.693
persley

00:05:27.474 --> 00:05:31.194
a little salt

00:05:46.060 --> 00:05:49.640
a little spicy oil 

00:05:49.640 --> 00:05:51.640
if you like it

00:05:58.680 --> 00:06:02.940
cover it and let cook for 20 minutes

00:06:03.694 --> 00:06:06.054
it's ready!

